# Generates assets/demo.gif — run with: vhs assets/demo.tape
Output assets/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 860
Set Height 540
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set Framerate 15

Hide
Type "source ./assets/demo-render.sh"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type `claude "How can I get more stars for https://github.com/asweigart/pyperclip?"`
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5.5s
